Titolo: Club Drive

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Club Drive is a racing video game developed and published by Atari Corporation exclusively for the Atari Jaguar on November 28, 1994, and later in Japan by Mumin Corporation on March 24, 1995.The game is set in the titular amusement park of the same name in the year 2098, where driving became legalized after being deemed illegal for safety reasons years prior due to the invention of indestructible vehicles, which allowed the ban to be lifted. Being one of the first titles announced for the Jaguar before it was officially launched to the public in November 1993, Club Drive was developed by most of the same personnel at Atari Corp. who worked on Alien vs Predator by Rebellion Developments, which was released a month prior.Club Drive received mixed to negative reception when it was released. As of April 1, 1995, the game has sold nearly 14.000 copies though it is unknown how many were sold in total during its lifetime.

